Privacy Policy for Bithaka App

1. Introduction
Welcome to the Bithaka App. This privacy policy explains how we collect, use, share, and protect your personal information when you use our app, designed to facilitate private classes between students and teachers.

2. Information Collection

Personal Information: We collect personal details such as name,  and  number when you register on our app.

Usage Data: We collect information on how you interact with our app, including access times, viewed pages.
3. Use of Information

To Provide Services: We use your information to connect you with teachers or students, schedule classes, and process payments.
Communication: We may use your contact details to send updates about the app or respond to your inquiries.
Improvement: Usage data helps us to improve the app functionality and user experience.
4. Information Sharing and Disclosure

Third-party Services: We may share your information with third-party services for payment processing ,
Legal Requirements: If required by law, we may disclose your information in response to legal processes or to protect our rights.
5. Data Security
We implement security measures to protect your data from unauthorized access, alteration, or destruction.

6. Changes to This Policy
We may update this policy periodically. The updated version will be posted on our app.

7. Contact Information
For any questions or concerns regarding this privacy policy, please contact us at [insert contact info].
